Interface Schematic

All Superinterfaces:
ArchetypeVolume, BiomeVolume, BiomeVolume.Mutable<ArchetypeVolume>, BiomeVolume.Streamable<ArchetypeVolume>, BlockEntityArchetypeVolume, BlockEntityArchetypeVolume.Mutable<ArchetypeVolume>, BlockEntityArchetypeVolume.Streamable<ArchetypeVolume>, BlockVolume, BlockVolume.Mutable<ArchetypeVolume>, BlockVolume.Streamable<ArchetypeVolume>, EntityArchetypeVolume, EntityArchetypeVolume.Mutable<ArchetypeVolume>, EntityArchetypeVolume.Streamable<ArchetypeVolume>, LocationBaseDataHolder, LocationBaseDataHolder.Mutable, MutableVolume, Volume
public interface Schematic extends ArchetypeVolume, LocationBaseDataHolder.Mutable
A special archetype volume designed to be persisted. Contains additional metadata to assist with this persistence.
